io.github.hjuergens.time

Class ScheduleBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.hjuergens.time.ScheduleBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScheduleListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class ScheduleBaseListener
extends Object
implements ScheduleListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of ScheduleListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
